terms.title: Counterintuitive
terms.Text: Contrary to intuition or to common-sense expectation (but often nevertheless true).

terms.title: Emotion Matrix
terms.Text: The dimensions of pleasant-unpleasant and helpful-harmful emotions lead to a 2X2 emotion matrix with 4 quadrants that illustrates the experience and influence of emotions on athletes.
